Ernie Newton (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ernie_Newton_(actor) 0 Ernest Newton (October 2, 1925–April 4, 1996) was an American actor and voice actor who has been seen and heard in several roles including that of Pierre the French Parrot in the Disneyland attraction Walt Disney's Enchanted Tiki Room.
